author: Martinisal
review-description: Seller communicated clearly to set expectations, worked with me to get the result I was looking for. Highly recommend! The project I asked for was converting my wifes character from an MMO we play into the anime style graphic, and I got exactly what I was looking for. I'm going to frame a print of it as one of my wifes Christmas gifts.
